data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom 2 bath home built in 2009. This property is perfect for a family looking to purchase their first home or be used as an investment property. Big open kitchen. Comes with a solar lease system with Better Earth Electric, buyers will need to take over the contract. Large backyard. Central AC. Enclosed fence. With a little work you can make this home your own.   Buyer will need to purchase this property in as is condition. Listings in this area don't last in this market. See you in escrow!
